Call TEXTE(6028,GBOUTS) From OBJDIV
Call TEXTE(12276,GBOUTP) From OBJDIV
Call TEXTE(16134,GBOUTA) From OBJDIV
Onkey   2 Titled GBOUTS Call S_CLB(zc) From W1PTEVAL0
Onkey 144 Titled GBOUTP Call P_CLB(zc) From W1PTEVAL0
Onkey 146 Titled GBOUTA Call SA_CLB(zc) From W1PTEVAL0
Gosub _AFF
